<inglise> COUNCIL REGULATION (EEC) No 1992/93 of 19 July 1993 transferring the financing of certain aids provided for in Regulations (EEC) No 1096/88 and (EEC) No 2328/91 from the EAGGF Guidance Section to the EAGGF Guarantee Section and amending Regulation (EEC) No 2328/91 as regards part-financing of the system to encourage the set-aside of arable land </inglise>
<eesti> N&Otilde;UKOGU M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (EM&Uuml;) nr 1992/93 millega antakse &uuml;le m&auml;&auml;rustega (EM&Uuml;) nr 1096/88 ja (EM&Uuml;) nr 2328/91 etten&auml;htud teatavate toetuste rahastamine Euroopa P&otilde;llumajanduse Arendus- ja Tagatisfondi (EAGGF) arendusrahastult EAGGF tagatisrahastule ning muudetakse m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 2328/91 p&otilde;llumaa tootmisest k&otilde;rvalej&auml;tmist soodustava s&uuml;steemi osalise rahastamise osas 19. juuli 1993 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COUNCIL OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE N&Otilde;UKOGU, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Economic Community, and in particular Article 43 thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa Majandus&uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, eriti selle artiklit 43, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the proposal from the Commission (1), </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse komisjoni ettepanekut, (1) </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the opinion of the European Parliament (2), </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa Parlamendi arvamust (2) </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, in order to replace the aid schemes provided for in Titles II, VII and VIII of Council Regulation (EEC) No 2328/91 of 15 July 1991 on improving the efficiency of agricultural structures (3), new schemes financed by the European Agricultural Guidance and Guarantee Fund (EAGGF) Guarantee Section were introduced by Council Regulation (EEC) No 2078/92 of 30 June 1992 on agricultural production methods compatible with the requirements of the protection of the environment and the maintenance of the countryside (4) and by Council Regulation (EEC) No 2080/92 of 30 June 1992 instituting a Community aid scheme for forestry measures in agriculture (5); </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: selleks et asendada n&otilde;ukogu 15. juuli 1991. aasta m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 2328/91 (p&otilde;llumajandusstruktuuride t&otilde;hustamise kohta) (3) II, VII ja VIII jaotisega etten&auml;htud toetuskavad, on n&otilde;ukogu 30. juuni 1992. aasta m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 2078/92 (keskkonnakaitsen&otilde;uete ning paikkondade alalhoiuga koosk&otilde;las olevate p&otilde;llumajanduslike tootmisviiside kohta) (4) ja n&otilde;ukogu 30. juuni 1992. aasta m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 2080/92 (p&otilde;llumajanduse metsastamismeetmetega seotud &uuml;henduse abikava kohta) (5) kehtestatud uued kavad, mida rahastab Euroopa P&otilde;llumajanduse Arendus- ja Tagatisfondi (EAGGF) tagatisrahastu; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, in order to replace the aid schemes provided for in Council Regulation (EEC) No 1096/88 of 25 April 1988 establishing a Community scheme to encourage the cessation of farming (6), new schemes financed by the EAGGF Guarantee Section were introduced by Council Regulation (EEC) No 2079/92 of 30 June 1992 instituting a Community aid scheme for early retirement from farming (7); </inglise>
<eesti> selleks et asendada n&otilde;ukogu 25. aprilli 1988. aasta m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 1096/88 (millega kehtestatakse &uuml;henduse kava p&otilde;llumajandustegevuse l&otilde;petamise soodustamiseks) (6) etten&auml;htud toetuskavad, on n&otilde;ukogu 30. juuni 1992. aasta m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 2079/92 (millega seatakse sisse talupidajate ennet&auml;htaegse vanaduspensioni &uuml;henduse abikava) (7) kehtestatud uued kavad, mida rahastab EAGGF tagatisrahastu; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the 1992 harvest is the last for which new applications may be made to participate in the set-aside scheme referred to in Article 2 of Regulation (EEC) No 2328/91; whereas this scheme is financed equally by the Guarantee and Guidance Sections of EAGGF; </inglise>
<eesti> 1992. aasta saak on viimane, mille kohta v&otilde;ib esitada uusi m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 2328/91 artiklis 2 osutatud maa tootmisest k&otilde;rvaldamise kavas osalemist k&auml;sitlevaid taotlusi; k&otilde;nealust kava rahastavad v&otilde;rdselt EAGGF tagatis- ja arendusrahastu; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas new forms of set-aside have been introduced by Council Regulation (EEC) No 1765/92 of 30 June 1992 establishing a support system for producers of certain arable crops (8), and by Regulations (EEC) No 2078/92 and No 2080/92; whereas these new forms of set-aside are financed by the Guarantee Section of the EAGGF; </inglise>
<eesti> n&otilde;ukogu 30. juuni 1992. aasta m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 1765/92 teatavate p&otilde;llukultuuride tootjatele toetuss&uuml;steemi kehtestamise kohta (8) ning m&auml;&auml;rustega (EM&Uuml;) nr 2078/92 ja (EM&Uuml;) nr 2080/92 on kehtestatud uued maa tootmisest k&otilde;rvaldamise meetodid; selliseid uusi maa tootmisest k&otilde;rvaldamise meetodeid rahastab EAGGF tagatisrahastu; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas it transpires from the transitional provisions laid down for Article 11 of Regulation (EEC) No 2078/92, Article 11 of Regulation (EEC) No 2079/92 and Article 8 (1) of Regulation (EEC) No 2080/92 that expenditure may continue to arise under the old schemes provided for in Regulations (EEC) No 2328/91 and (EEC) No 1096/88 after 1 January 1993; </inglise>
<eesti> m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 2078/92 artikliga 11, m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 2079/92 artikliga 11 ja m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 2080/92 artikli 8 l&otilde;ikega 1 etten&auml;htud &uuml;leminekus&auml;tetest selgub, et p&auml;rast 1. jaanuari 1983 v&otilde;ivad kulutused m&auml;&auml;rustes (EM&Uuml;) nr 2328/91 ja (EM&Uuml;) nr 1096/88 s&auml;testatud endiste kavade kohaselt suureneda; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the transfer from the old to the new schemes should be facilitated while preventing the simultaneous existence of two different administrative schemes; whereas provision should therefore be made for financing of all expenditure on such measure effected by the Member States from 1 January 1993 by the Guarantee Section of the EAGGF; </inglise>
<eesti> &uuml;leminekut endistelt kavadelt uutele tuleks lihtsustada, v&auml;ltides samal ajal kahe eri halduskava samaaegset kehtimist; seep&auml;rast tuleks ette n&auml;ha, et k&otilde;ik liikmesriikide poolt alates 1. jaanuarist 1993 tehtud k&otilde;nealuse meetmega seotud kulutused rahastab EAGGF tagatisrahastu; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas all expenditure incurred by the Member States from 16 October 1992 on in respect of the various set-aside measures should be placed under the same heading in the financial perspective; whereas Regulation (EEC) No 2328/91 should be amended accordingly, </inglise>
<eesti> k&otilde;ik liikmesriikide poolt alates 16. oktoobrist 1992 tehtud maa tootmisest k&otilde;rvaldamise eri meetmetega seotud kulutused tuleks paigutada samasse finantsperspektiivi rubriiki; m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 2328/91 tuleks vastavalt muuta, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> Expenditure incurred by the Member States from 1 January 1993 on schemes provided for in Titles II, VII and VIII of Regulation (EEC) No 2328/91 and in Regulation (EEC) No 1096/88 shall be eligible under the Guarantee Section of the EAGGF. </inglise>
<eesti> Liikmesriikide poolt alates 1. jaanuarist 1993 tehtud m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 2328/91 II, VII ja VIII jaotisega ning m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 1096/88 etten&auml;htud kavadega seotud kulutusi v&otilde;ib rahastada EAGGF tagatisrahastu. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> Regulation (EEC) No 2328/91 is hereby amended as follows: </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolevaga muudetakse m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 2328/91 j&auml;rgmiselt: </eesti>
<inglise> 1. the following sentence shall be added to the last subparagraph of Article 1 (2): </inglise>
<eesti> 1. artikli 1 l&otilde;ike 2 viimasele l&otilde;igule lisatakse j&auml;rgmine lause: </eesti>
<inglise> 'However, for expenditure incurred by Member States on this scheme from 16 October 1992 on, the Community contribution shall be covered in its entirety by the Guarantee Section of the EAGGF on the basis of the rates fixed pursuant to Article 31 (2). </inglise>
<eesti> "Liikmesriikide poolt k&auml;esolevale kavale alates 16. oktoobrist 1992 tehtud kulutuste puhul kaetakse &uuml;henduse osamaks t&auml;ielikult EAGGF tagatisrahastust artikli 31 l&otilde;ikes 2 kehtestatud m&auml;&auml;rade alusel. </eesti>
<inglise> ' ; </inglise>
<eesti> &ldquo;; </eesti>
<inglise> 2. the following sentence shall be added to the second subparagraph of Article 31 (1): </inglise>
<eesti> 2. artikli 31 l&otilde;ike 1 teisele l&otilde;igule lisatakse j&auml;rgmine lause: </eesti>
<inglise> 'However, expenditure incurred by the Member States in respect of the measures from 16 October 1992 on shall be eligible only under the Guarantee Section of the EAGGF. </inglise>
<eesti> "liikmesriikide poolt alates 16. oktoobrist k&otilde;nealustele meetmetele tehtud kulutusi v&otilde;ib rahastada ainult EAGGF tagatisrahastu." </eesti>
<inglise> Article 3 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 3 </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall enter into force on the third day following its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus j&otilde;ustub kolmandal p&auml;eval p&auml;rast selle avaldamist Euroopa &Uuml;henduste Teatajas. </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus on tervikuna siduv ja vahetult kohaldatav k&otilde;ikides liikmesriikides. </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Brussels, 19 July 1993. </inglise>
